<mvc:View 
    controllerName="com.fiori.project01.controller.ProductDetail" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">
    <Page title="{i18n>detailPageTitle}">
        <content>
            <f:SimpleForm id="SimpleForm" editable="true" title="商品詳細">
                <f:content>
                    <Label text="商品名"/>
                    <Text id="name" text="{mProducts>name}"/>
                    <Label text="価格"/>
                    <Text id="price" text="{mProducts>price} {mProducts>currency}"/>
                    <Label text="原料"/>
                    <Text id="ingredients" text="{mProducts>ingredients}"/>   
                    <Label text="生産者"/>
                    <Text id="producer" text="{mProducts>producer}"/>                             
                </f:content>
            </f:SimpleForm>
        </content>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>